      "para_id": "Q001988.1",
      "line_range": "1",
      "translation": "(1) For Nintinuga , lady of the living and the dead , his lady , Enlil-bani , the powerful king , king of Isin , king of Sumer and Akkad , the beloved of Enlil and Ninisina , built the E-nidubu , his beloved temple ."
    }
  ],
